00:12:27.230 --> 00:12:31.620
What I like is
translating science,

00:12:31.620 --> 00:12:33.830
which is somewhere near
to the leading edge,

00:12:33.830 --> 00:12:35.795
into something that
consumers can buy.

00:12:35.795 --> 00:12:37.920
And I don't want to get
metaphysical with you here.

00:12:37.920 --> 00:12:40.670
But I think there are some
really fundamental things

00:12:40.670 --> 00:12:42.960
wrong with our
health care system.

00:12:42.960 --> 00:12:47.070
And we don't often enough
