00:24:22.340 --> 00:24:23.680
You learn from those.

00:24:23.680 --> 00:24:24.560
You incorporate.

00:24:24.560 --> 00:24:25.870
You speak to more consumers.

00:24:25.870 --> 00:24:28.630
You speak to more investors
that are expert in the space.

00:24:28.630 --> 00:24:30.620
And you modify your approach.

00:24:30.620 --> 00:24:33.045
So as all of you think about
building companies, products,

00:24:33.045 --> 00:24:34.670
and technology, think
about how are you

00:24:34.670 --> 00:24:36.490
getting it to the consumer.

