AUDIENCE: Mobile.

00:46:17.250 --> 00:46:18.190
RICH KIVEL: Mobile.

00:46:18.190 --> 00:46:21.540
Think about Google is the
mobile app in so many ways.

00:46:21.540 --> 00:46:22.110
What else?

